      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in impeccable mechanical condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, utilizing high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a fully inspected subframe and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers. Every kinematic component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to exacting standards. A true driver\u2019s machine with flawless synchros and a linear power band that remains the benchmark for naturally aspirated performance.",
