      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is the definition of 'showroom floor' quality. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating and zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and factory-fresh, showing absolutely no wear, complemented by original protective floor mats and a strictly smoke-free environment. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians, with all records organized in a comprehensive binder. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, this car offers a new-car experience for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
