      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and it is in truly stunning condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, smoke-free, and meticulously detailed. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on this beauty. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
