      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 engineering. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies, providing an 8,000 RPM redline and instantaneous throttle response. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox ensures tactile engagement, while the dual-VANOS system has been professionally bulletproofed. The chassis is structurally perfect, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a variable M differential lock that maintains optimal traction. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine interior, this car retains its factory-fresh damping and steering precision, making it a turnkey investment for the serious collector.",
